# Plan: AuroraFeedFlow — Full iOS/iPadOS RSS Reader

## Context
- Existing project: fresh SwiftUI boilerplate (AuroraFeedFlowApp.swift + ContentView.swift)
- Target: iOS + iPadOS, Swift 6, SwiftUI, Combine, CloudKit, CoreData
- Style goal: FEEED app — minimal, typography-first, magazine article reader

